profile_positions.description:
• Responsible for the aggregated & detailed demand and supply planning of all products for the Netherlands retail and out-of-home market
• Management responsibility over the demand planning team (7 FTE), 
• Executional leader in the Sales & Operations Planning process to deliver and facilitate accurate sales forecasting, optimal inventory levels and maximum customer service levels, in collaboration with the Marketing Directors and the Sales directors
• Responsibility over short, mid & long term forecasting, supply planning and subcontracting planning & execution;
• Supply & network planning from our  international factories (Europe) and 3rd party suppliers across the world (Europe & Asia);
• Key contact person within the supply chain team for the management teams of the two business units (Retail and Out-of-home);
